Package: morphology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Morphological description of low-dimensional categorical arrays
Description: The {morphology} package implements a flexible API for the
    calculation of nearest-neighbour based morphological quantities for
    one-, two- or three-dimensional categorical arrays.
